Stallion Motors – Hyundai and LG have rewarded a loyal customer with an LG Dual cool high end AC Unit in Lagos. The reward is coming following a raffle draw promotion initiated by both companies. At the end of the raffle draw, Mr Ebun Sofunde San won the AC unit which was presented to his representative in Hyundai showroom in Victoria Island, Lagos recently. Stallion Group Company, Hyundai Motors registered high sales in 2019 and was awarded the highest selling brand in the new car segment. The group remains committed to providing the best-in-class service and a complete range of world-class vehicles to the Nigerian consumers. Stallion’s Automobiles Division consists of a collective sub-group of companies which represent an array of globally renowned automobile brands on an exclusive basis for distribution, sales and aftersales service. Stallion represents the following brands through independent management: Honda, Hyundai, Nissan, Volkswagen, Porsche, Audi, Skoda, Changan, Ashok Leyland. Collectively these brands contribute to over 45 per cent share of the new automobiles market in Nigeria. For over 25 years, Stallion has worked closely with its auto OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturers) partners to develop the industry and bring global best practices and a unique brand experience to customers in Nigeria at par with the developing world. It is largely credited for opening exciting frontiers of motoring to the Nigerian people and providing them with first-hand experience of world-class automobiles throughout different model segments from passenger cars, SUVs, luxury vehicles, pickups, light commercial vehicles and buses.